Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The status of one who can't see the effort\Nof someone trying to protect something...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.63,0:00:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...is lower than this watchtower!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.30,0:00:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I have arrested the\Nviscount due to his interference.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.47,0:00:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Standing by at the watchtower.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.51,0:00:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The assistant was injured...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.18,0:00:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me your injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.06,0:00:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't going to hide it from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause you'd get mad if I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.82,0:00:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.08,0:00:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This just now was...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.42,0:00:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I did it without permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.51,0:00:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.76,0:01:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The next time I touch you,\NI will tell you before I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.35,0:01:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time, please tell me how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.28,0:01:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear me, Shirayuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.54,0:01:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, shall we head back?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.29,0:01:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be dark soon, so we should hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.18,0:01:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.05,0:01:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,To leave a girl like that around\Nwith no social status to speak of...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.64,0:01:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's trickery...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.73,0:01:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiki, Zen will bring that girl with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.53,0:01:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.70,0:02:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.54,0:02:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.18,0:02:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Her hands... are hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.43,0:02:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen's voice that had called\Nmy name over and over
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.89,0:02:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,was tinged with warmth, and lit\Na fire in a color I hadn't seen before...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.32,0:04:15.49,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Episode 11: Encountering...\NA Color for the First Time"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.83,0:04:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do, Shirayuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.87,0:04:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,For the prince's party to\Naccompany just me to the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.54,0:04:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't last if you're that nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.00,0:04:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But Shirayuki, it's the prince! The prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.21,0:04:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Kihal!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.72,0:04:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.\NAre you ready to leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.18,0:04:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, your highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.39,0:04:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the fastest way from here to Yuris island\Nwould be to go through this mountain pass
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.60,0:04:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and come out along the coast.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.85,0:04:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Calmly...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.23,0:04:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Calmly... So no one will\Nthink anything is strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.36,0:04:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I think that will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.07,0:04:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki, are you here to see Kihal off?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.57,0:04:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Y-Yeah, th-that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.37,0:04:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How's your injury?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.62,0:04:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's fine. Ryu's treating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.66,0:05:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.58,0:05:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think Shirayuki's been\Nstrange since the bird handler test?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.38,0:05:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. But Zen looks the same as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.63,0:05:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the strange part.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.55,0:05:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen said or did something, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.26,0:05:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What did he--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.18,0:05:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you all gathered around for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.31,0:05:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We're leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.60,0:05:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.81,0:05:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw man, I wanted to go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.78,0:05:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Leaving that aside...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.49,0:05:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Miss, when you and the master\Nwere alone together at the watchtower...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.95,0:05:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...did he scold you harshly?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.12,0:05:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:05:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, he didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.08,0:05:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not. That's not what it was, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.09,0:05:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.96,0:05:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I have to get to work. See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.26,0:05:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wait... Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.10,0:06:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, it's hard to get anything out of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.27,0:06:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's wrong with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.94,0:06:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been three days already,\Nso I thought I'd have calmed down by now,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.99,0:06:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,but when I saw Zen's face,\NI got flustered again...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.74,0:06:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.83,0:06:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This is different from everything\NI've told Zen up until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.79,0:06:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen, what should I tell you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.35,0:06:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to use the birds as a means\Nof communication for the kingdom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.94,0:06:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Kihal took the test as\Na representative bird handler.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.53,0:06:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,As a result, we decided to implement the system.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.61,0:07:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, we will acquiesce\Nwith your demand to protect the birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.83,0:07:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,However, we would like some of your\Npeople to come to the castle with the birds
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.83,0:07:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,to train the soldiers in how to handle them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.75,0:07:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.59,0:07:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...true?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.30,0:07:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,For you, who have been\Nclashing with the hunters,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.92,0:07:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe it will be hard for you to accept\Nthe proposition of the kingdom, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.89,0:07:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you show us something\Nto make us trust your sincerity?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.89,0:07:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The apology of Lord Brecker,\Nand ten million dil in acquiescence money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.69,0:07:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what we request.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.69,0:07:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.07,0:07:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That is what he says. Your highness?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.82,0:07:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do what I can to obtain\Nthe viscount's apology,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.57,0:07:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,but ten million dil, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.03,0:07:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Kiki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.49,0:07:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, if we prepare twice that,\Ndoes that mean you will agree to the terms?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.75,0:07:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If we use money to buy authority\Nand make you obey,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.76,0:07:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,we will be no different from the viscount.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.30,0:08:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not believe that the sincerity\Nyou desire will come from that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.52,0:08:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.48,0:08:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I have spoken disrespectfully, your highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.81,0:08:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Please allow us to work with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.61,0:08:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we're counting on you on our end, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.28,0:08:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.37,0:08:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.58,0:08:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a real prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.87,0:08:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stop, you little--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.29,0:08:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, I'm the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.75,0:08:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! A prince! Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.13,0:08:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's the castle like?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.76,0:08:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,--When are you going back?\N--Do you wanna eat some, Prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.26,0:08:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Kids, you can have an audience\Nwith the prince one at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.68,0:08:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,--His retainer!\N--The real thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.81,0:08:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a sword! A sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.52,0:08:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What do they mean by "the real thing"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.48,0:08:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He did a fine job of seeing through us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.15,0:09:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought all nobility\Nand royalty were the same,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.32,0:09:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,but he appears to be completely\Ndifferent from the viscount.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.91,0:09:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.92,0:09:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking a walk, your highness?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.34,0:09:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,May I join you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.34,0:09:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You can stop talking like that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.30,0:09:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.35,0:09:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Kiki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.43,0:09:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I invited her, but she left it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.56,0:09:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Left what to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.14,0:09:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen, did something happen\Nbetween you and Shirayuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.94,0:09:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Something happened, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A kiss... I kissed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.03,0:09:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.28,0:09:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.20,0:09:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? It wasn't a dream or anything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.46,0:09:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't dream that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.21,0:09:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And? What did Shirayuki say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.34,0:10:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't say anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.55,0:10:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.84,0:10:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't respond?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.35,0:10:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She looked surprised and turned red.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.14,0:10:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl did?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.22,0:10:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What? It wasn't a dream\Nor an illusion or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.56,0:10:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She turned red...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.23,0:10:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I have had feelings\Nfor Shirayuki for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.74,0:10:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,When I touched her... I became sure of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.75,0:10:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to tell her that as a prince of Clarines.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.42,0:10:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen, I'm sure she...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.88,0:10:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.26,0:10:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.43,0:10:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't serve you just because\Nyou're Prince Zen of Clarines, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.44,0:10:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.40,0:11:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I've cooked the riko fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.99,0:11:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, then grind it.\NI'll weigh the rudra leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.70,0:11:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.53,0:11:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Miss, Ryu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.95,0:11:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We're preparing a medicinal tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.96,0:11:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The chief herbalist has had consecutive\Nall-nighters, so her stamina is at its limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.63,0:11:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of that, she's in a bad mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.92,0:11:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we give her\Ndelicious tea, she'll be nicer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.34,0:11:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're making it? Not just giving her tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.18,0:11:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we make medicines here,\Nwe're going to make medicinal tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.28,0:11:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.03,0:11:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's bitter and sour!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.99,0:11:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What if we dissolved\Njulia flowers and rock sugar in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.79,0:11:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll lose half its efficacy if we do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.33,0:12:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to mix in something\Nthat produces similar effects...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.17,0:12:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What about roka?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.08,0:12:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.92,0:12:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It smells similar, and it's sweet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.80,0:12:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never steeped it\Nin hot water before, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.15,0:12:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to do work...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.95,0:12:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you able to sleep a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.91,0:12:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.91,0:12:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief herbalist, here's some roka tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.91,0:12:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Roka tea...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.37,0:12:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It smells good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.34,0:12:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.34,0:12:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This would be good to steep in\Nanti-inflammatory medicines for kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.22,0:12:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the perfect sweetness for\Ncutting the bitterness of medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.60,0:13:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Are there are a lot of\Nkids who don't like medicine?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.11,0:13:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, I can't believe you\Nguys thought to make roka tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.57,0:13:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Obi thought of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.82,0:13:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.74,0:13:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.24,0:13:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, you went to the\Nroka garden with Shirayuki and Ryu, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.12,0:13:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it was nothing.\NJust a thought from an amateur.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.45,0:13:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think Shirayuki and Ryu would've been\Nable to make this roka tea by themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.54,0:13:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a good influence on each other, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.75,0:13:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you keep close the things\Nthat can widen your perspective, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.49,0:13:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki, once you're\Ndone with that, you can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.61,0:13:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What, already?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.62,0:13:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we've done more\Nthan enough for today already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.70,0:13:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But... um, if I don't\Nconcentrate on something...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.50,0:14:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...it'll be bad... I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.84,0:14:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What will?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.59,0:14:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? S-Something will...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.55,0:14:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki, if you're worried about something...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...you should write it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I even made Ryu worry. It's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.87,0:14:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let things continue like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.96,0:14:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I need...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.54,0:14:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I need some time to think by myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.06,0:14:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The forest...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.76,0:14:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? You want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.55,0:14:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, if I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.72,0:14:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's not being used for training,\Nit should be okay to go in...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.72,0:15:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I take you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.44,0:15:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though it's on the\Ncastle grounds, it's still far...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.36,0:15:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... She's not talking at all anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.66,0:15:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.08,0:15:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Master, and everyone! You're back early.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.67,0:15:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we're right on schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.05,0:15:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you guys?\NWhat're you doing all the way out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.18,0:15:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.30,0:15:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Miss. Why are you hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.26,0:15:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It was so sudden... I was surprised...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.35,0:15:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.77,0:15:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Miss, run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.69,0:15:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.27,0:15:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,--What?\N--It's fine, just hurry! Run to the forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.78,0:15:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.53,0:15:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She ran away, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.41,0:15:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you told her to!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.12,0:16:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.79,0:16:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who made her\Nwant to run, didn't you, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhide, Kiki, Obi. I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.09,0:16:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait at the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.22,0:16:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Prince Zen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.60,0:16:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh... What should I do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.11,0:16:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I ran without thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.65,0:16:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did I do something so pointless...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.32,0:16:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.91,0:16:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I can't face you right now, Zen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.46,0:16:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.58,0:16:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't chase you, so please stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.09,0:16:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.30,0:16:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.26,0:17:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, normally, {\i1}I'd{\i0} be the\None that can't face you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? No, that surprised me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.19,0:17:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it the part where I said\Nto tell me how you feel next time?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The first time we met was in a forest, too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.51,0:17:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki, why don't we stay\Nhere together for a little bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.39,0:17:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.06,0:17:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. The talks with\Nthe bird handlers went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.65,0:17:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.73,0:17:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to form the squad after this,\Nso Kihal will probably come to the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.24,0:18:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind that blows through\Nover there feels the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.08,0:18:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen, do you come to this forest often?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.16,0:18:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? In the past I did, to take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.83,0:18:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But after I started coming in\Nand out to practice riding,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.42,0:18:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,it stopped being a place where I could relax...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.38,0:18:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I don't come that much anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.09,0:18:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I like the forest outside better.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.05,0:18:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.05,0:18:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, you're here,\Nso it's different, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.76,0:18:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Just that is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.11,0:18:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a nice sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.86,0:18:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.36,0:18:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It was then that I realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.49,0:18:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,After meeting Zen and spending time with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.37,0:18:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,In the feelings that\NI continuously faced Zen with...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There were still emotions that I hadn't found...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.55,0:19:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.14,0:19:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, Zen...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.98,0:19:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so dear to me, and I respect you,\Nand I want to be your strength, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.19,0:19:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I realize that I'm in love with you, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.70,0:19:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.83,0:19:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if it's okay to want to look\Nat you the same way as I have until now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.51,0:19:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I want that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.52,0:19:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki, the royal title I hold\Nmay not be able to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.56,0:20:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how much I will be able to\Ngive back in return for what I get from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.32,0:20:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But even so, I want to be with you from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.66,0:20:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish for you to be by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.20,0:20:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear, upon our meeting...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.29,0:20:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I will protect the desires\Nof us both with my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.71,0:20:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to do so, it might be\Nstrange to ask you to help me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.63,0:20:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but you certainly give me strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.89,0:20:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you take this hand, Shirayuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.91,0:20:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Prince Zen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.50,0:20:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something\NI've thought about for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.59,0:21:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since I found out that my own\Nsocial status sometimes constrains others,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.67,0:21:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't help but think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.10,0:21:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mitsuhide.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.60,0:21:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.85,0:21:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What if someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.48,0:21:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I found a person dear to my heart\Nand wanted to be with them...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.48,0:21:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,When that person responds to my feelings,\Ndo you think I can believe
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.69,0:21:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that it's a response from their heart...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.11,0:21:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That it's not something they are\Nsaying because they cannot disobey me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.78,0:21:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Will I be able to believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.16,0:21:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I will ever be able to\Nmeet someone who I can believe needs me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.13,0:21:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Shirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.76,0:21:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen's voice that called\Nmy name was tinged with warmth
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.14,0:21:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and lit a fire in my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.27,0:22:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki's eyes trembled kindly
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.27,0:22:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and lit a fire in my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.16,0:22:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, I'm sure time after time...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.78,0:22:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...time after time, the warmth of this day...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.87,0:22:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...the memory of this day...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.33,0:22:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...will give me courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.16,0:24:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Open Castle Day?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.00,0:24:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.25,0:24:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm not use to stuff like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.00,0:24:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best. We're here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.63,0:24:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes! The climax of today's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.69,0:24:20.08,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Episode 12: Goodbye to the Beginning"
